data.title: Have it all.
data.meta_description: Dell Technologies is the leader in digital transformation, providing digital technology solutions, products, and services to drive business success.
data.text:
^Purchase any XPS, Inspiron, Alienware, Latitude, Precision, Optiplex, or monitor between 29th July 2024 and 26th September 2024 and Dell Technologies (Headquarters: One Dell Way, Round Rock, Texas 78682, USA) will donate US $1.75 for each eligible product within your purchase order to Computer Aid (33 Foley St, London W1W 7TL, UK). Dell Technologies supports Computer Aid and, based on global sales, will make a total minimum donation of US $1,000,000.00 and up to a maximum donation of US $1,200,000.00 to support Computer Aid’s efforts to bridge the digital divide and to improve the lives of disadvantaged people using digital technologies. Dell’s donation will include laptops, monitors, headsets, desktops, and other technology equipment worth approximately US $750,000, which will go toward the minimum and maximum donation amounts. Offer applies to purchases on Dell.co.uk only (excluding Dell Outlet). Not valid for Dell outlet, resellers and/or online auctions. Items may ship separately. Terms and Conditions of Sale and Service apply, see www.dell.co.uk/terms. Dell Services do not affect consumers’ statutory rights. Dell is not responsible for typographical, pricing or other errors. Dell reserves the right to cancel orders arising from any errors or stock availability.

**Rewards: Rewards are earned on Dell purchases (excluding Dell Outlet purchases and third party products) made on dell.co.uk. Find out all information on Dell Rewards Program.

XBOX Game Pass Important Details: Offer applies on select gaming PCs only. Credit card required. Unless you cancel, you will be charged the then current regular membership rate when the promotional period ends. Terms, exclusions, and streaming limits apply. Xbox Cloud Gaming (Beta): select devices and regions. After term, active membership required to play games and online multiplayer. Game catalogue varies over time, region, and by device. DLC sold separately; if a game is removed from catalogue or your membership ends, you will need to purchase the game separately to use your DLC. If you’re already an Xbox Live Gold and/or Game Pass for Console/PC member, any days remaining in your membership(s) will be converted to Ultimate using a conversion ratio. Future code redemptions also subject to conversion ratio. All conversions to Ultimate are final. Details and system requirements at Join Xbox Game Pass: Discover Your Next Favourite Game | Xbox . Offer valid in all Xbox Game Pass markets excluding Russia. Digital Direct: Your digital content will be delivered directly to your device during set-up; no codes required.

Onsite Service After Remote Diagnosis and Other Important Information: *Onsite service is determined by technician and cause of issue; may involve customer access to inside of system and multiple or extended sessions. If issue is covered by warranty and not resolved remotely, technician or part will be dispatched, usually within 1-2 business days following completion of remote diagnosis. Onsite service is provided by Dell Marketing L.P. Availability and terms vary by country and by product. For complete details see Dell.com/service contracts.

Onsite availability varies by country and service purchased. Onsite service available after remote diagnosis on field serviceable units.

3. Pricing: The pricing available on this site is Dell’s pricing for online purchases only. No discounts apply to Dell’s online pricing other than the savings listed on this site. Any promotional savings listed on this site are referenced off of a previous online price for the same product or service. If you have contractual terms with Dell that refer to list pricing, please contact your Dell sales representative to obtain information about Dell’s list pricing.
